description: A body was discovered after an Air France flight had arrived in Paris from Ivory Coast.
title: 'Child stowaway' found dead in plane's undercarriage in Paris
title_page: 'Child stowaway' found dead in plane's undercarriage in Paris - BBC News
maintext: The body of a child aged about 10 has been found in the undercarriage of a plane that had arrived in Paris from Abidjan, sources close to the investigation have told French media.
